high_descs: Turn left, go to wall.  Turn left to face table.
Pick up knife from right side of table.
Turn around to face counter between sink and microwave.
Place knife in left side of sink, left of the mug.  Turn water on, fill sink, empty sink, turn water off.  Remove knife from sink.
Turn around, go half way down table on right.  Turn right to face table.
Put knife on table, sticking into tomato in middle of table.
anns.task_desc: Get knife, clean knife, put in apple on table.

high_descs: Turn to the left then walk forward. Turn to the left again and face the table.
Pick up the yellow knife off of the table.
Turn around and walk forward to the sink.
Place the knife in the sink and then wash it. Take the knife out.
Turn around completely and walk forward. Turn left to face the table.
Place the knife on the table in front of the pepper.
anns.task_desc: Wash the knife in the sink and put it away.

high_descs: Turn to the left, go to the door, hang a left and go to the white table.
Pick up the yellow handled knife that is on the table.
Turn around and go to the sink.
Put the knife in the sink, rinse it off, then pick it back up.
Turn around, go to the white table on the right where the tomato is.
Put the knife in the tomato that is on the table.
anns.task_desc: Put a clean knife in a tomato.
